quran[7{c,v,t}:
33,44,jis roz woh is se milein ge un ka tohfa ( khuda ki taraf se ) salam hoga aur is ne un ke liye bara sawab tayyar kar rakha hai
33,45,ae paighambar hum ne tum ko gawahi dainay wala aur khushkhabri sunanay aur darane wala bana kar bheja hai
33,46,aur khuda ki taraf bulanay wala aur chairag roshan
33,47,aur mominoun ko khushkhabri suna do ke un ke liye khuda ki taraf se bara fazl hoga
33,48,aur kafiroon aur mnafqon ka kaha nah maanna aur nah un ke takleef dainay par nazar karna aur khuda par bharosa rakhna. aur khuda hi karsaaz kaafi hai
33,49,momino! jab tum momin aurton se nikah karkay un ko haath laganay ( yani un ke paas jaane ) se pehlay Talaq day do to tum ko kuch ikhtiyar nahi ke un se adt poori karao. un ko kuch faida ( yani kharch ) day kar achi terhan se rukhsat kardo
33,50,ae paighambar hum ne tumahray liye tumhari biwiyan jin ko tum ne un ke mohar day diye hain halal kar di hain aur tumhari londiyan jo khuda ne tum ko ( kufar se bator maal ghanemat ) dilwai hain aur tumahray chacha ki betiyan aur tumhari phupiyon ki betiyan aur tumahray mamoon ki betiyan aur tumhari khalaon ki betiyan jo tumahray sath watan chore kar aayi hain ( sab halal hain ) aur koi momin aurat agar apne tain paighambar ko bakhash day ( yani mohar lainay ke baghair nikah mein aana chahay ) bashart e kay paighambar bhi un se nikah karna chahain ( woh bhi halal hai lekin ) yeh ijazat ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) khaas tum hi ko hai sab musalmanoon ko nahi. hum ne un ki biwion aur londion ke baray mein jo ( mohar wajib alada ) muqarrar kardiya hai hum ko maloom hai ( yeh ) is liye (kiya gaya hai ) ke tum par kisi terhan ki tangi nah rahay. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
